00:11:43,564 --> 00:11:49,312
iz geven a kvitsheray. hob ikh nokh dem gehert far vos zi hot gekvitshet, vayl zi hot getrofn dem ABA.

199
00:11:49,403 --> 00:11:55,320
er iz geven mit di zun bay undz in lager. der alter mentsh hot gehat oykh a BAKH- a zun,

200
00:11:55,326 --> 00:11:56,434
a BAKHUR.

201
00:11:56,845 --> 00:12:00,467
a ben hot er ⟨m-⟩ nisht aleyn iz er geven, oykh a ben, KEN.

202
00:12:00,642 --> 00:12:02,391
iz er geven mit im.

203
00:12:02,886 --> 00:12:06,052
zey hobn gemakht beyde SHI- LESHAKHRER.

204
00:12:06,244 --> 00:12:09,680
iz bay ⟨d- v-⟩ bay di zun, ikh bin nisht geforn keyn mol.

205
00:12:09,838 --> 00:12:11,992
kh'hob afile nisht gevust vu er voynt.

206
00:12:12,387 --> 00:12:14,068
nor bay di

207
00:12:15,002 --> 00:12:17,038
alte mentsh fleg ikh geyn.

208
00:12:15,745 --> 00:12:17,949
a, ir hot im ⟨br-⟩ bakent?

209
00:12:18,006 --> 00:12:23,110
ikh hob im gekent. nokh fun di lager ikh hob im gekent. KEN, BETAKH.

210
00:12:22,461 --> 00:12:24,227
un andere mentshn?

211
00:12:23,980 --> 00:12:28,040
LO, andere nisht. nor dem, nor dem hob ikh gekent.

212
00:12:24,537 --> 00:12:26,134
⟨,⟩ froyen?

213
00:12:28,418 --> 00:12:33,390
andere mentshn kh'hob gekent, ober zey, ale mentshn zenen gegangen voynen, ikh veys nisht vu AFILU.

214
00:12:33,784 --> 00:12:35,702
nor im hob ikh gevust.

215
00:12:35,809 --> 00:12:39,700
hob ikh gef- emetser hot mir gezogt zayne KTOVET,

216
00:12:39,775 --> 00:12:41,996
un azoy bin ikh gegangen bay im.

217
00:12:42,810 --> 00:12:45,456
biz ven ⟨er iz⟩ UNK ⟨gekumen⟩...

218
00:12:43,622 --> 00:12:47,986
ir gedenkt, gute mentshn vos hobn geholfn

219
00:12:48,769 --> 00:12:51,935
in lager, in, MAKHANOT,

220
00:12:52,366 --> 00:12:53,366
..

221
00:12:52,498 --> 00:12:54,618
vos ir kent dertseyln?

222
00:12:54,979 --> 00:13:00,592
LO. andere mentshn veys ikh nisht bikhlal, gute.

223
00:13:02,387 --> 00:13:04,760
un ir hot emetsn geholfn?

224
00:13:05,593 --> 00:13:10,734
vos hot men gekent helfn in di lager? m'hot nisht gehat gornisht. mit vos hot men gekent helfn?

225
00:13:10,875 --> 00:13:16,550
a! a mol, ven ikh hob gearbet, alts, SABALIT... ⟨S- vi azoy iz dos?⟩ SABALIT...

226
00:13:16,562 --> 00:13:19,576
fleg ikh geyn, hob ikh gebrengt kartofl

227
00:13:21,085 --> 00:13:28,140
un,... andere zakhn nisht. hob ikh arayngeleygt do a kartofl, tsvey, zol ikh emetsn kenen gebn. m'hot geleygt

228
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:31,401
SENDVITSHIM oyf di broyt, azoy vi me leygt vursht.

229
00:13:31,401 --> 00:13:34,461
azoy hobn di mener nebekh gegesn azoy:

230
00:13:34,872 --> 00:13:36,654
kartofl geshnaydt,

231
00:13:36,863 --> 00:13:41,860
oyf di broyt geleygt. ot dos hob, ven kh'hob gekent hob ikh bahaltn

232
00:13:41,860 --> 00:13:45,670
⟨un ge⟩trogn far d- a mol dem man, a mol dem man geholfn.

233
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:47,352
zey hobn gearbet nokh shverer.

234
00:13:48,152 --> 00:13:52,440
di mener hobn gearbet shverer nokh vi di froyen. BETAKH.

235
00:13:52,422 --> 00:13:55,010
 un ⟨d-⟩...

236
00:13:53,552 --> 00:13:55,710
azoy. epes andersh, neyn.

237
00:13:55,864 --> 00:14:02,237
eyn mol hob ikh geholfn... TOV, dos iz vayl ikh hob nisht lib gehat, NAKNIK fun, DAM,

238
00:14:02,395 --> 00:14:06,442
fun blut. ikh hob dos nisht gekent esn, vi hungerik ikh bin geven.

239
00:14:06,442 --> 00:14:12,940
ikh hob dos avekgegebn far, andere meydelekh, vos zey hobn geven mit mir in eyn, blok gevoynt,

240
00:14:12,940 --> 00:14:14,032
