241
00:14:14,393 --> 00:14:18,538
⟨ikh hob⟩ gegebn dos. ober ikh hob nisht gekrign a tsveyte zakh vegn dos.

242
00:14:18,882 --> 00:14:20,445
⟨ikh hob dos⟩ avekgegebn.

243
00:14:21,210 --> 00:14:22,937
du host shoyn gegesn a mol?

244
00:14:22,937 --> 00:14:25,558
UNK nisht yeder ken dos esn,

245
00:14:26,003 --> 00:14:28,191
NAKNIK fun DAM.

246
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:31,701
⟨dos⟩. epes andersh ikh hob nisht gehat vos tsu helfn.

247
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:34,215
vos hob ikh gekent helfn?

248
00:14:34,153 --> 00:14:40,050
un, ⟨do ir⟩, in Erets-Yisroel, ir zent, tsufridn?

249
00:14:40,617 --> 00:14:46,162
yo. nu, BETAKH. az m'iz gekumen aher darf men zayn tsufridn.

250
