MISHTARA finef yor...

254
00:15:05,068 --> 00:15:12,600
MISHTARA? finef yor UNK BINYAN un andere pletser, nor dernokh dem iz er arayn in KHEVRAT KHASHMAL.

255
00:15:12,949 --> 00:15:16,605
ober azoy, ikh bin tsufridn. ale mol ikh bin a tsufridene.

256
00:15:16,628 --> 00:15:19,609
kh'vil ⟨nisht⟩ zayn a raykhe, kh'veys nisht vi raykh.

257
00:15:20,475 --> 00:15:24,910
⟨kh'bin⟩ tsufridn yetst oykh. di kinder kumen. KEN.

258
00:15:26,944 --> 00:15:27,944
⟨⟩.

259
00:15:27,057 --> 00:15:35,336
