MAKOM vegn tsu makhn dos.

264
00:15:58,680 --> 00:16:01,380
hot zi mir gemakht YOM HULEDET.

265
00:16:03,253 --> 00:16:08,420
nu, ikh hob keyn mol nisht geshlogn mayne meydelekh. mayn man hot a mol geshlogn.

266
