 vos?

276
00:16:24,988 --> 00:16:28,149
ir hot epes funem, bafrayt

277
00:16:28,149 --> 00:16:31,445
funem lager, ir vilt undz tsaygn? yo.

278
00:16:29,713 --> 00:16:33,830
nu, ikh hob dir gevizn, ikh hob a tsetl gehat, aha.

279
00:16:33,949 --> 00:16:36,271
